"    Decreased nuclear lobes in myelodysplasia (pseudo Pelger-Huet anomaly)",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 356px; height: 245px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
