"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?4/45/4821/abstract/5\">",
"      van den Bent MJ, Wefel JS, Schiff D, et al. Response assessment in neuro-oncology (a report of the RANO group): assessment of outcome in trials of diffuse low-grade gliomas. Lancet Oncol 2011; 12:583.",
